{"id":92090,"title":"Trench foot: a relatively rare condition in tropical countries - a case report.","abstract":"Trench foot is a relatively rare condition in tropical countries. We present here a case report of trench foot in a child who was put on hip spica for her hip ailment. Although rare, awareness on the part of the clinician can prevent this potentially serious condition and early diagnosis and treatment can prevent further consequences. ","date":"2014-03-20","categories":"Wounds and Injuries","split":"train","url":"http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/24448485","annotations":[{"name":"Disease","weight":0.750676,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Disease"},{"name":"Diagnosis","weight":0.73221,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Diagnosis"},{"name":"Therapy","weight":0.699927,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Therapy"},{"name":"Medical diagnosis","weight":0.682664,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Medical_diagnosis"},{"name":"Case report","weight":0.20545,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Case_report"},{"name":"Foot","weight":0.201782,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Foot"},{"name":"Clinic","weight":0.164972,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Clinic"},{"name":"Child","weight":0.0805305,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Child"},{"name":"Tropics","weight":0.0557163,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Tropics"},{"name":"Rare disease","weight":0.0422207,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Rare_disease"},{"name":"Awareness","weight":0.0391252,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Awareness"},{"name":"Trench foot","weight":0.0297972,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Trench_foot"},{"name":"Hip","weight":0.0248395,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Hip"},{"name":"Country","weight":0.0227187,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Country"},{"name":"Trench warfare","